citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1pm on
19-Jun-19.
From 1 PM to 1:30 PM the inspector waited at the facility and called the cell phone number on file leaving a
message.
